Title: Conformal Foliations and Constraint Quantization
Authors: J.N. Tavares
Comments: 24 pages, Latex
Journal-ref: J.Geom.Phys. 18 (1996) 381-402
\\
  We show that the Classical Constraint Algebra of a Parametrized Relativistic
Gauge System induces a natural structure of Conformal Foliation on a
Transversal Gauge. Using the theory of Conformal Foliations, we provide a
natural Factor Ordering for the Quantum Operators associated to the Canonical
Quantization of such Gauge System.
